'From Squeak2.8alpha of 16 February 2000 [latest update: #2217] on 26 May 2000 at 4:30:32 pm'!"Change Set:		WnldFix-arDate:			26 May 2000Author:			Andreas RaabFixes the end of stream problem."!!WonderlandCameraMorph methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'ar 5/26/2000 15:51'!sketchOn: aCanvas	| vtx prev next |	vtx _ ReadStream on: self outline vertices.	vtx atEnd ifTrue:[^self].	prev _ vtx next.	[vtx atEnd] whileFalse: [		next _ vtx next.		aCanvas line: prev to: next width: 5 color: Color red.		prev _ next]! !